title: Bronze OCE Players
body:
I'm terrible at League, hence I'm in bronze. I'm looking to play with fellow bronze players in Oceania. Looking to climb honestly and just have fun, I get bored playing League by myself so add me on League itself or here or even twitter (twitter.com/Sealisanerd)  Top lane main mostly but willing to learn other roles :)
(IGN: Atteactiveseal)

replies.body: Hey, I would be down to play. Im bronze 1. add me :) I ADC main.
I'm not ranked but I'll likely be in bronze this season! it'd be nice to flesh out my friends list again (IGN is Wess)
Hey, im also bronze. If you're ever up for a game just add me in client (Ign is Fossiled)
